Create files:

touch Networking/notes.txt
touch Linux/commands.txt
touch Reports/report.txt

Copy file:

cp Networking/notes.txt Linux/

Move file:

mv Linux/notes.txt Reports/

Rename file:

mv Reports/notes.txt Reports/linux_notes.txt

Delete file:

rm Reports/linux_notes.txt
Command Purposes
Command	Purpose
touch	Creates new file
cp	Copies files
mv	Moves or renames files
rm	Deletes files
